### Core Technologies
- **Plasmo**: Chrome extension framework (v0.90.5)
- **React 18**: UI framework with TypeScript
- **Tailwind CSS**: Styling framework
- **MCP (Model Context Protocol)**: AI tool integration system

### Project Structure
- **Entry Points**: [background.ts](mdc:src/background.ts) (service worker), [content.tsx](mdc:src/content.tsx) (content script), [sidepanel.tsx](mdc:src/sidepanel.tsx) (side panel)
- **Configuration**: [plasmo.config.ts](mdc:plasmo.config.ts) (build config), [package.json](mdc:package.json) (dependencies)
- **Core Libraries**: [src/lib/](mdc:src/lib/) (shared components and utilities)
- **Features**: [src/features/](mdc:src/features/) (extension features)
- **MCP Integration**: [src/mcp/](mdc:src/mcp/) and [src/mcp-servers/](mdc:src/mcp-servers/) (AI tool system)

### Key Features
- AI-powered tab management and organization
- Browser automation with natural language commands
- Research assistance and content summarization
- Price comparison across websites
- 80+ MCP tools for extended functionality

### Build System
- **Development**: `pnpm dev` - starts Plasmo dev server
- **Build**: `pnpm build` - builds for multiple browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari)
- **CSS**: `pnpm build:css` - compiles Tailwind CSS

### Browser Support
- Chrome/Edge: Manifest V3
- Firefox: Manifest V2
- Safari: Compatible build
